1. Put this folder into recipes-kernel of meta-$(bsp-board)
2. In file build/conf/local.conf add the belows line 
    MACHINE_ESSENTIAL_EXTRA_RDEPENDS += "kernel-module-nrf24l01"
3. Run bitbake $(image). Whose IMAGE_FEATURE has dev-pkgs.
4. For loading nrf24l01 kernel, we need run the belows commands
    modprobe nrf24l01
